        .about.span3
          %h2 About Us
          %p Dayhome Registry is your answer for all of your dayhome searching needs!
          %p Being a parent is busy enough. The mission of Dayhome Registry is to make being a parent a little easier.
          %p 
            %a= link_to 'Read More...', about_pages_path
        .contact.span3
          %h2 Contact Us
          %p Have any questions or concerns about Dayhome Registry? We'd love to hear from you.
          %p
            Email us at
            %a{:href => "mailto:contact@dayhomeregistry.com"} contact@dayhomeregistry.com
